You can connect to the INFN machine using SSH. From a Linux terminal you can use:

ssh elixir-it-trein.recas.ba.infn.it

You can find below usernames and passwords. They will be available in this file until tomorrow 17th May 2017 at 2pm CET (12h GMT).
All software has been installed on the machine. Therefore, we strongly recommend you start testing it as soon as you can. Should you have any problems, you can write to Giacinto (giacinto.donvito@ba.infn.it) or Stefano (stefano.nicotri@ba.infn.it).
